item.title: Stack Overflow Blows Past 10 Million Questions
item.description:
Even more impressive, 7.5 billion page views:

If a dev found a solution just half of those times, and it saved them just 30 minutes, that’s nearly 1.85 billion hours saved.

What a mind blowingly helpful resource for developers around the globe.
